message.content: The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are: cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DL. The paper discusses a modular system for question answering via REST API, which involves natural language processing, document search, and reading comprehension. These topics are closely related to computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and deep learning (cs.DL).
